OOC: 3 Guesses as to whom DM is dealing with? And the first two don't count.

::DarkMouse::

She went to the lab and started looking at the DNA samples. She noticed one 
that said a certain bot's name on it. She smiled and remembered her old 
leader.  "Yeah, she was a good leader. Too bad she was killed by that damned 
rattlesnake bot."  She went looking around just to cure bordom.  Then she 
remembered her old experiment.  She went rushing over to the CR tanks and 
peered inside them.  They were all empty.  She sighed and guessed the 
experiment had been trashed.  Then she turned and was about to leave, when 
she saw the cloning tank.  She looked inside it and saw what she was looking 
for. It was a perfect replica of her former leader. She smiled and double 
checked the process on the console. It had been completed, but no one had 
ever activated the bot.  She couldn't hold her excitement in any longer. She 
yelled out,"YES! IT'S BEEN SITTING HERE AND IT'S JUST FINE!" She went about 
checking all the programs and making sure that everything was in order. "Oh 
yeah, things will get better when she's re-awakened. Oh my leader, you will 
rise again."
